Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就告訴小穹好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越快越好不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用不著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  怪難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
