Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:18.99,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,10)\blur5}鳥之穹鳴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什麼大事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹出院的日子提前了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  穹還是第一次來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛摸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我沒摸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想摸吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在說什麼啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  冷靜點  可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才開始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和奈緒…交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在忙嗎  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩這點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就…做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  脫線了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你緊張什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  詳細希望詳細希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹睡覺時是睡衣派？還是連身裙派？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始我們正要開始交流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不充電一點預備知識的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼保護人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著你保護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對根本就不准你這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日野君真是個好哥哥呢  對穹來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  也沒你說得那麼了不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙生過病  身體也嬌小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚也白皙細膩  真的好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹雪白的肌膚也隨你想看就看的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  她是我妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  我開玩笑的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑也該有個分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他們是兄妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許有什麼奇怪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  你到這兒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…  我在想事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃  奈緒好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和奈緒是姐弟就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣就能每天吃到這些美味了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弟弟的話就不做這便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是小悠所以才做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這週大概會在委員會這些地方忙得不可開交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有一陣沒法一起回家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償  我們星期日見面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話也叫上小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫上穹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們兩個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  這會是我們第一次約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了…個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這打扮算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖了個淋浴之後  人涼颼颼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你興奮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦  笨蛋  你太沒防備了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我又不會給悠以外的人看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼話  也不要給我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定是在挑逗我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我  現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒怎麼…只是看你白天好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來很沒精神？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  搬來這裡以後有很多事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想小悠你也一定累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這週日也不必勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  不過我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也有擔心過穹習不習慣上學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她好像也交上朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以週日我們好好地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼樣  描述一個弱小游泳部的女孩們奮鬥歷程的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  小悠你不會只是想看女主角穿泳裝的樣子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以好好地期待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次約會  讓我們好好點綴起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹果然有夠可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無可奉告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又什麼都沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我放心了  她交到了亮平以外的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  就算不用我操心  穹是不是應該也能自己前行了…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說些什麼大叔式的對白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吧  我是代替雙親的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一時  她會漸漸離開我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  後天怎麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天？  週日？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好過什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了啊  你說一起去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上上週
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說班上的同學戴著可愛的髮飾  還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這回事來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒記筆記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒記…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不好意思  我有預定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼預定？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  不過你會回絕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可很期待後天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:27.00,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（悠  對不起我說謊了\N不過是悠不好\N誰叫你想和那種女人親和）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等我到現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想跟你邊聊聊邊回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我根本就沒想到你會等我  真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天天氣會很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近明明每週都下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿什麼衣服好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠你怎麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個…我還完全沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就把我們的顏色搭一搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一模一樣的話也太張揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用差不多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼顏色好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好決定呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那淡藍色系怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能協調又不顯眼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…明天的約定我沒能推掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償  下週我會好好陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能先忍過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果悠決定選那邊的話我就死心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上如果你改主意了  就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先  立正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定跑得很匆忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正公車走了  那就步行過去Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  昨晚沒怎麼睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為第一次約會而緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次約會一定得讓我好好安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就滿心期待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給穹應該很配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去挺適合她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大出血了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的炸薯餅  用來做晚飯應該很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎肉和毛豆炸薯餅  每樣兩件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這不太像約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  為小穹操勞的小悠總會顯得非常溫柔  我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以現在過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做炸薯餅咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道小穹現在還喜歡吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  睡著了嗎  我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的狀態不太好  今天就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點小事而已  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠丟下我  一個人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  怎麼可能會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過嗎  我們是相依為命的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  對不起  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來後睡一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會替你煮好咖哩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹病好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天買晚飯的菜時偶然遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  本想為你們煮咖哩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去  我還只能慢慢地走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  要是陪著我們就會遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來小穹是不會認同我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小穹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「才不把哥哥讓給你！」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直對我頤指氣使  毫無尊敬我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…好喜歡你  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…悠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:50.02,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}待續
