Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.53,0:25:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.75,0:25:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.33,0:25:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠留在我裡面
